{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01SrzS6X2h8wwgXwiJekpJzu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The cluster is running in insecure mode with `--insecure` flag. I need to:\n\n1. Generate CA, node, and client certificates using the openssl-toolbox pod\n2. Create Kubernetes secrets with those certificates\n3. Update the StatefulSet to:\n   - Remove `--insecure` flag\n   - Add `--certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs`\n   - Mount the certificate secrets into pods\n\nLet me understand the CockroachDB TLS setup:\n- Need a CA certificate\n- Need node certificates for each pod (or a wildcard/common node cert)\n- Need a client certificate for the root user\n\nCockroachDB has built-in certificate generation via `cockroach cert` commands, which should be simpler than using openssl directly since the binary is already in the pods.\n\nI'll use one of the running pods to generate the certificates, then create a Kubernetes secret from them and update the StatefulSet. The node certificate needs to cover localhost, 127.0.0.1, and each pod's DNS name within the cluster.\n\nGenerating certificates with cockroach cert...\n\nThen I need to copy those certs out of the pod using kubectl, create Kubernetes secrets for both the node certificates and client certificates, and finally update the StatefulSet to enable secure mode with the certificates mounted as volumes.\n\nI should also update the liveness and readiness probes to use HTTPS instead of HTTP, and keep in mind that the existing data in the PVCs will persist through this transition from insecure to secure mode.\n\nNow I'm laying out the execution plan: generate certificates using the cockroach cert command on one of the pods, copy them locally, create the Kubernetes secrets, update the StatefulSet configuration to remove the insecure flag and mount the certificate directory, then perform a rolling restart and verify everything is working.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1959,"cache_read_input_tokens":29249,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1959},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c6f031ef-2901-4af0-8311-4a44140e01e3","uuid":"f252624c-ff2d-4293-97c5-d6bc70dadd1b","request_id":"req_011CcLZjrErTaY4caVwWBc1u"}
